  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 15.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Standing for hours.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nobody said anything.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't know what will happen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After a few hours, when we've been already so tired and-- so they took us to the washroom.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We-- they-- we had to undress quickly and naked.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then they put us in big bins, 10 in a very dirty something water.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then naked we came out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Men came and took all the hair from everywhere, naked as we've been.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They was laughing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Anyway, and then when we've been half-frozen, so they gave us a remnants of Russian prisoner of war things what left over, which was like a shirt-type and pants.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Often the-- the shirt and pants didn't have any button or just one button or so.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So sometimes girls had to hold onto it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Beg pardon?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That-- they took it away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then they selected and they send that to Germany.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Beg pardon?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That kind of a-- it was-- it was a green-colored cotton shirt.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Mine didn't have a-- a button here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the pants, I didn't have a button here.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I hold on to it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And later on, we started to dig in the bed or in the mattress, which was very low, and digged in.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I for good luck found two pieces of string, so I straight away had at least something so I didn't have to hold it so strong together.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the first day, we didn't do anything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They just left us there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the barracks.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But then it came, the counting.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] In the morning, they woke us up about 3 o'clock, [NON-ENGLISH] for the counting, because the German woman, there was very primitive prostitutes and thieves and murderers.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they didn't know the counting to do.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
